title: Subtitle Finder 1.7
description:
SubFind 1.7 
                     - Subtitle Finder -

Search subtitles in 8 sites at the same time.

SubFind description:

SubFind was developed in order to search subtitles in multiple web sites at the same time.
The aim is to save time for user and enable him to find the wanted subtitle in the 
shortest time. The integrated browser in the program opens all sites and lists the results in its interface. The important point is here to be indicated is the listing is done only from the first of the result pages. Since the program works as a normal browser, it does not occupy the bandwidth of the sites in vain.

It is impossible to download the listed subtitles by the program.
However when you make a double click on the chosen subtitle on the list the default
browser of the user opens the related download page of the web site of which the subtitle presents, as a new window page.
During the search it is aimed to list the information as much as possible. However the information of some sites may be in different pages.
In this kind of conditions when you click on the lines written "Get info" or "Get FPS" it is possible to get information about that subtitle.

PLEASE SEED WHEN YOU FINISH THE DOWNLOAD.

Enjoy!!
